{"tid":20414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日睇返 梁天琦應該endorse熱普城而唔係青政","createTime":"2016-12-03T10:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T17:23:59.000Z","uid":2748,"like":21,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"05b4b70969b3c9f2b50dc97673189d5014bb3a52","tid":20414,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:51:45.000Z","msg":"假設無假票 熱普城點都執返三席 而本民前同熱普城又唔會處於敵我關係 即使做唔到盟友都唔會互相攻伐<br />\n青政就繼續搶游離泛民票<br />\n民族黨繼續搞教育同外交 同熱普城處於友好關係<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇返 根本梁天琦當時唔撚應該支持青政 而係支持熱普城 只要強調港獨同制憲可以雙軌並行就可以"},{"pid":"6df5f3345bd3feff6a53db5ce2a3511c251637a0","tid":20414,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"07318ed8da8152247271a7ec8f5caa3125fffb31","tid":20414,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:13:20.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"84d5d9fbfd8bb66bc72ecf18e0f23ef054fa5af4","tid":20414,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:15:41.000Z","msg":"一子錯"},{"pid":"1aeeee03d565995cdfa3b64a3558ea96b3fd07d8","tid":20414,"uid":4722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:17:07.000Z","msg":"根本就係<br />\n當初熱普城五區插哂旗<br />\n識做咪黎endorse一齊搞永續基本法<br />\n係要自己起壇搞對台(好似lihkg咁）<br />\n最後仆街唔好喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce4a06db85537bfc83395544a73e2380e3c31bc","tid":20414,"uid":30669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:19:55.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b4be993b27339abde10b1ffa58cb077c12787059","tid":20414,"uid":20670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:22:09.000Z","msg":"無啦 馬後炮絕無意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4fb6df2df71d15470d5343a36f6fef34c89a19","tid":20414,"uid":11830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:23:00.000Z","msg":"無掌權都日日話清算<br />\n<br />\n掌到權仲得了？"},{"pid":"e7e2da8995788b2aa5d19ebebd92